      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个云原生架构下的CQRS事件流时序图。核心流程是：Aggregate产生事件后存入Event Store，然后有个Reactor组件把事件转成异步任务推到Queue里，最后Queue Worker去执行具体的Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我梳理一下参与者顺序：Aggregate → Event Store → Reactor → Queue → Queue Worker → Side Effect，这样从左到右排列可以吗？还有Reactor和Queue Worker是两个独立的worker角色对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Reactor是监听事件并生成任务的，Queue Worker是消费队列的，职责要分开。另外Side Effect执行完要有成功和失败两种分支，成功的话标记任务完成，失败要支持重试。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：Aggregate向Event Store发送Store Event，Event Store dispatch给Reactor，Reactor push job到Queue，Queue把job分配给Worker，Worker最后去Execute Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，dispatch和push这两个动作要区分清楚，一个是事件分发，一个是任务入队。还有Worker和Side Effect之间的交互，应该是Worker调用Side Effect，然后Side Effect返回结果给Worker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整了，现在Reactor到Queue是Push Job，Queue到Worker是Process Job，Worker到Side Effect是Execute Side Effect。接下来画成功和失败的分支，用alt块可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，alt块里Success分支：Side Effect返回Success给Worker，Worker标记Job为Completed；Failure分支：返回Failure，Worker触发Retry Job。注意箭头方向都是回到Queue Worker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成。我检查一下：六个参与者，主流程五步，alt分支覆盖成功标记完成和失败重试两种场景。CloudNative_DockerImage的标注也加在图注里了，整体符合事件驱动加队列解耦的设计。",
